### 创建场景 - 削峰填谷
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/scenes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sceneName": "削峰填谷-白天充电晚间放电",
  "scenarioType": 1,
  "stationId": 1,
  "enabled": true,
  "priority": 1,
  "description": "在电价低谷期充电，高峰期放电",
  "rules": [
    {
      "conditionType": 1,
      "conditionSign": 2,
      "thresholdValue": "80",
      "action": "开始放电"
    },
    {
      "conditionType": 2,
      "conditionSign": 1,
      "thresholdValue": "50",
      "action": "限制功率"
    }
  ]
}

### 查询场景详情
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/scenes/1

### 查询电站下场景列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/scenes/station/1

### 删除场景
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/scenes/1
